comments.body: I think it would be better if you try to flash the unit first because sometimes this kind of issue can be fixed by flashing or updating it to the latest firmware or try SD card flashing.If it didn't work then we are sure that is a hardware issue based on your logs the 3rd hashboard only detects a few ASIC chips so if you want to continue mining you need to remove the 3rd hashboard.Or like other newbies did to fix this kind of issue without the BGA hot-air tool they put this broken hashboard into the oven for 15 minutes.
